 Most bees in mkjh-vault use MIT; some stay private — check with
 Queen's LICENSE philosophy before deciding.)_

For private bees, the Queen's license applies (see vault-root LICENSE).
For public bees, choose one of:

- MIT (simple, permissive) — https://choosealicense.com/licenses/mit/
- Apache-2.0 (permissive + patent grant) — https://choosealicense.com/licenses/apache-2.0/
- AGPL-3.0 (copyleft for networked services) — https://choosealicense.com/licenses/agpl-3.0/

When decided, replace this file's contents with the chosen license text,
with the correct year and name (Mike Holmsted / mkjh.dk).
